locality: Ankarana Special Reserve, N sector, Sentier botanique on E side of Ambilobe-Antsiranana Hwy. (RN 6), ca. 47 km N of Ambilobe.
Antsiranana: E sector of Ankarana Nat. Park, 0.4 km (air) NW of village of Mahamasina (at entryway to park along RN 6).
Forest patch 19 km south of Antsiranana on road to Ambilobe.
